highlights.text: “Is It Over Now? (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” by Taylor Swift is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #1.
“I Wonder” by Kanye West is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 24 spots at #116.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Is It Over Now? (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” is the highest at #1.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 180 weeks straight.
